About this property

The Royal Heritage Villa is the best budget home Stay property situated conveniently in the center of the New City of Udaipur in a non-tourist neighborhood, yet within a short distance from all major attractions of Udaipur. It has nice ambience and spacious rooms.

There is 1 bookable suite room with attached bathroom,balconey, small sitting area seperate from bed room area, Television, Air conditioner,a double bed, a Single Jharokha bed, a Single Couch/Lounger bed and a Sofa. It can accomodate up to 4 guests.
